<div class=WordSection1>

<center><h1> ARTO - Analysis of Replication Timing and Organization </h1></center>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>Software
implementation for the algorithm used to analyze ToR data in:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left'><b><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>Systematic
determination of replication structure highlights interconnections between
replication, chromatin structure and nuclear localization,</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>Shlomit
Farkash-Amar, Yaara David, Andreas Polten, Hadas Hezroni, Yonina C. Eldar, Eran
Meshorer, Zohar Yakhini and Itamar Simon</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left'><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:
"Times New Roman","serif"'>ARTO</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:
"Times New Roman","serif"'>In this website you can download a MATLAB
implementation of ARTO (Analysis of Replication Timing and Organization). The
software takes raw time of replication (ToR) measurement signals as input and
outputs for each genomic location an estimate of its ToR and an association to
CTR (constant ToR region) or TTR (Temporal Transition Region).  Please see
figure below. Please read the description of input and output parameters for
most efficient use of the software.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:
"Times New Roman","serif"'>When using this SW please cite <u>Farkash-Amar et
al.</u> </span></p>
<img width=576 height=294 id="Picture0" src="image001.jpg"
alt="real_data_segmentation_example.png">
 
<p class=MsoCaption align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left'><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif";color:windowtext;font-weight:normal'>An
example of ARTO segmentation result of chromosome 15 in replicate 2 of mouse
lymphoblasts (L1210). Raw data in red, segmented data in regions defined as
CTRs or TTRs in black, and in gray – undefined regions where only ToR is
determined.</span></p>
<p><br></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:
"Times New Roman","serif"'>Downloadable files:</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>
<a href="ARTO.m" onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('/downloads/ARTO.m'); ">
ARTO - MATLAB implementation</a></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>
<a href="ARTO_running_example.m" onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('/downloads/ARTO_running_example.m'); ">
Running Example</a></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>
<a href="ARTO_running_example_data.mat" onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('/downloads/ARTO_running_example_data'); ">
Data for the running example</a></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>Description
of input and output parameters</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>Inputs to
the SW are:</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>locs</span></i><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'> – a row vector containing the
genomic locations of the measured probes.</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>signal
</span></i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>– a row vector
containing the raw ToR measurements data (should be the same length as <i>locs</i>).</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>fork_rate
</span></i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>- a two-elements
vector of the fork-rate range in [Kb/min].</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>Sphase_length
</span></i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>– S-phase length
in [hours].</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'> <i>num_reps</i>
– number of replicates used in one algorithm run. (optional input).</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>W</span></i><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'> – window length. Default value
is 120. (optional input)</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>min_seg_length</span></i><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'> –<i> </i>minimal number of
points voting for a linear line. Note: the algorithm allows less points if
their vote is higher. Default value is 10. (optional input).</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>min_seg0_length
– </span></i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>minimal number
of points voting for a linear line. Default value is 10. (optional input)</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:
-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>plot_hist_flag</span></i><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'> – a flag indicating whether to
plot the histograms of segment length (in bp) and of fork-rate per probe. Default
value is false. (optional input)</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>Outputs
of the SW are:</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>SegSignal</span></i><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'> – the ToR of each genomic
location, after the segmentation. (same size as <i>locs</i>)</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>BreakPoints<span
dir=RTL></span><span dir=RTL><span dir=RTL></span> </span></span></i><span
lang=HE dir=RTL style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>– </span><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>genomic location of breakpoints
between segments.</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle align=left style='text-align:left;
text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>CTIndicator
</span></i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>– a cell array
which indicates if the genomic location is part of a CTR (‘C’), a TTR (‘T-‘ or
‘T+’) or undefined (‘UD’). (same size as <i>locs</i>)</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:
-18.0pt;line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span dir=LTR></span><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>ForkRateVec
</span></i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>– an array of
the inferred fork-rate for each probe. (same size as <i>locs</i>)</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;
line-height:150%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left'><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>&nbsp;</span></p>

</div>

